Create list of 2D PCs

Source: R/make2DPCs.R
make2DPCs.Rd

Create list of 2D PCs

make2DPCs(pca_output, ref, which_pcs, vis_sd)

Arguments

pca_output

Output from gm.prcomp
ref

Reference face
which_pcs

Which PCs are to be created. Single number or vector, maximum allowed is 3
vis_sd

Extent of desired manipulation in units of standard deviation

Value

A list of 2D coordinates for the reference face at -vis_SD and |codevis_SD standard deviations for each principal component

Examples

data(LondonSet_aligned)
data_aligned <- LondonSet_aligned
pca_output <- geomorph::gm.prcomp(data_aligned)
ref <- geomorph::mshape(data_aligned)
make2DPCs(pca_output, ref, which_pcs = 1:3, vis_sd = 1.5)
